- Pravá identita učitele Kima.

18
00:00:56,330 --> 00:00:57,600
Je doktor Boo Yong Joo.

19
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,360
Je to tak, že?

20
00:01:00,030 --> 00:01:01,100
Viďte?

21
