66
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:55,030
Tahle operace se za žádnou cenu 
nesmí uskutečnit.

67
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,460
Dr. Kang tam stále je, že?

68
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,860
Prosím?

69
00:04:04,130 --> 00:04:05,730
Už to vzdejte.

70
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:08,000
Je to on, že?

71
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:10,230
Dr. Boo Yong Joo.

72
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:13,700
Ano?

73
